show.description: Katie heartlessly abandoned her boyfriend Sean because she looked down on his lack of wealth. Years later, Sean becomes a young CEO and stands before Katie. He wants her to see her mistake in choosing, but he gradually realizes that the girl before him has actually always loved him.
